title: Awal Mohammed impresses to help Raja Casablanca to a 3-1 victory over Fus Rabat
text:
09:55 CET Awal Mohammed impresses to help Raja Casablanca to a 3-1 victory over Fus Rabat - www.ghanasoccernet.com 
Ghana defender Awal Mohammed was a pillar at the back to help Raja Casablanca to a 3-1 victory over Fus Rabat in the Moroccan FA cup first leg. 
Awal,27, has had a smooth start to life in Casablanca having been involved in Raja's last seven games. 
For more Ghana football news visit www.ghanasoccernet.com
